text: Value for money place to eat with decent food. Not too large variety of food choices but as good as it gets in the area. Four stalls, including a Drink Stall, Economical Rice Stall, Noodle Stall, and Indian Muslim Stall.
The Auntie selling the drinks always not in the mood. Maybe have anger issues or problems. I observe shes not fine with the other races.

The aunty selling the always with anger
Not even know how make tea c
The place seemed a little warm but the breakfast set is still good.
You must try the curry chicken noodle. Very generous portion of meat and noodle. The disadvantage is very limited parking lot available.
